
: Public vs Private vs Friends vs Groups
: every element can be completely private (ie only that user sees it)
: if page is set to private then a default private page is shown (not user specific)
: if public element then visible to all other users
: if friends element then only visible to friends
: if groups, then user can select, on a per-element basis, a set of users that can see

Page
├── Metadata
│   ├── Slug/URL (required)
│   ├── Created timestamp (required)
│   └── Last updated (auto-managed)
│
├── Identity
│   ├── Name (required)
│   ├── Avatar (optional)
│   └── Tagline (optional)
│
├── About
│   └── Bio (optional - container exists but can be empty)
│
├── Presence
│   ├── Contact (optional)
│   └── Links (optional array)
│
└── Content
    └── (optional array of content blocks/sections)